{"tid":1599130,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"口號建議 容港自治","createTime":"2019-09-27T20:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T11:05:45.000Z","uid":90520,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"38a1a6a31a7f9ba31d8819864eb114ba0d206a45","tid":1599130,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:34:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因果由國 容港自治</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果用呢句 我諗受眾會更多更廣</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">原因有幾個啦</span><br />\n首先呢句 係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">誠哥</span></span>畀我地<br />\n有足夠份量去support呢句<br />\n就好似 我地叫光復香港 都會諗起天琦咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二 自治呢個字眼 接受程度點都好過獨立<br />\n一個口號要大家都講 首先係要大家都認同<br />\n高度自治呢個 不嬲都係核心價值<br />\n係香港 咩階層都會認同<br />\n<br />\n三 呢句野 大家都識接<br />\n因為大家都聽過講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n四 呢句野 真係對準政權<br />\n講到明<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因果由國啊</span></span><br />\n仲表達到訴求添 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自治</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一登報嗰陣 我就想提議<br />\n依架呢個時勢幾啱用"},{"pid":"09e88b15beae1b8471dce46be9bd0ff20c4af534","tid":1599130,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:35:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光</span>"},{"pid":"4cfbf21fbeed1555e8f53d5abd37025492bdaa7f","tid":1599130,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:35:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">復</span>"},{"pid":"301683603835f9591d298729f3fe225a8d32cf5c","tid":1599130,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB